Package: quickmatsums
Type: Package
Title: Quick matrix row/column sums using C++
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-10-09
Author: Raghav Sharma
Maintainer: Raghav Sharma <raghav.sharma1881@gmail.com>
Description: Uses C++ to perform perform row and column sums on a M x N matrix and returns a vector corresponding to the sums of all rows length M, or a vector corresponding to the sums of all columns length N.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.9)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
